{"tid":1634354,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"睇睇gphone個post 好嗎","createTime":"2019-10-07T07:36:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T09:05:34.000Z","uid":299729,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"0c4433a08dfe4b4a94c4ea7d808a326fccdfb175","tid":1634354,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:36:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/1023721804/posts/10216737697487827?sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F1023721804%2Fposts%2F10216737697487827%3Fsfns%3Dmo&d=fuRTyfFj%2BaUlIJflnhZSn96RZRvdwXM7zdVXDSHfEk0%3D&h=219aeaed\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/1023721804/posts/10216737697487827?sfns=mo</a><br />\n大家真係要睇睇呢個post<br />\n我之前都有諗兩會通過得嚟<br />\n總統簽得嚟 今年年尾都唔知得唔得<br />\n仲要中間存在好多變數<br />\n<br />\n仲有gphone喺comment覆咗過去四來，去過華盛頓四年來，未聽過Solomon Yue呢個人<br />\n我驚各連登仔被人水咗 佢有可能係共和黨<br />\n但未必係兩會議員 大家再fact check,好嗎？"},{"pid":"57446f877ec0c7fa2d1daba4e44034c5a16c055d","tid":1634354,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:36:20.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"eb021a2462a4775752eaf313274e1d0cdec2e4c4","tid":1634354,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:36:31.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"6351bbb32c352fd1ce1c3ca7ea10ebacac97b639","tid":1634354,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:36:41.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"4f55063f2778c4432c075ffb660fb3546a7953fb","tid":1634354,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:36:52.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"4033816ccad6ec1528ec4dfb3dbb9f1fdf67fe96","tid":1634354,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:37:20.000Z","msg":"5"},{"pid":"7fbaeb76d6f74347c39ec4b271b775f4290b5d4e","tid":1634354,"uid":299729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T07:37:49.000Z","msg":"6"},{"pid":"ee09fa3f95f56c9cec